\id 2TH - Mpoto Bible Version
\h 2 Bhasesalonike
\toc1 Baluwa ja kabhele jaka Paulo kwa Bhasesalonike
\toc2 2 Bhasesalonike
\toc3 2 Bhas
\mt2 Baluwa ja kabhele jaka Paulo kwa
\mt1 Bhasesalonike
\imt1 Ulongulelo
\ip Baluwa ja kabheli kwa Bhasesalonike jakalembakiki na Mtumi Paulo (Sula 1:1). Akalembiki baluwa jenu chikahi chijipi pena paakajomwili kujilemba ja kutumbula kwa Bhasesalonike iwezikana mu chaka cha 51 baada ja kubhelakeka kwaka Yesu Kristo. Paulo akabhi akona akabya mu muchi wa ku Kolinso paakalembiki baluwa jenu kwa likanisa lelakabhi ku Sesalonike, likanisa leakalitumbulili chikahi cha mwanja waki wa kabheli wa kiutumika (Matendu 17:1-10). Ilembakiki mu chitabu cha Matendu kubha likanisa haleli lakatumbuliwi na bhahobhalela bhakumu bhabhabhili na asili ja Kiyahude, na Bhayunani nde bhabhabhi bhamaheli.
\ip Ipwaghakika kubha likanisa la Bhasesalonike lakapaliki namaa kumanya mambu ghamaheli gha chikahi cha kujomukela na panani ja mambu gha kuhika kwaka Yesu mala ja kabheli, kwa kubha Paulo akalembiki ghamaheli kubhokana na lijambu leniheli mu baluwa yokapi ibheli kwa Bhasesalonike. Pambipi nusu jokapi ja baluwa ja kabheli jilongalela chikahi cha ujomukelu. Paulo kabhete alakalila kubhokana na ukata. Kila mundu impalika kuhenga lihengu nahuli kulipatila chilebhi (Sula 3:6-10).
\iot Ghaghabhihomu
\io1 Paulo atumbula kulemba baluwa jaki kwa kulimanyiha jombi mwene na bhajaki (Sula 1:1-2).
\io1 Kabhete Paulo anchengula Chapanga kwa ndandi ja likanisa lelibhi ku Sesalonike na kubhalobhela (Sula 1:3-12).
\io1 Paulo alongalela chikahi cha ujomukelu mkati ja Sula ja 2.
\io1 Kabhete Paulo alakalila ukata na kubhapwaghila bhandu kubha ibhapalika kutenda lihengu (Sula 3:1-15).
\io1 Kwa kujomulela, Paulo ajomulela kwa kubhalamukila kabhete (Sula 3:16-18).
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nepani Paulo, na Silivano na Timoseo.
\p Tundembela likanisa la ku Sesalonike, mwembi muka Chapanga Atati witu na Bambo Yesu Kristo.
\p 
\v 2 Chihomu na chibya kwinu, na lukwali yeihuma kwaka Chapanga Atati witu, na kwaka Bambo Yesu Kristo.
\s1 Utemulu chikahi cha kuhika kwaki Kristo
\p 
\v 3 Ndongu, itupalika kunchengula Chapanga chikahi chokapi kwa ndandi jinu. Ilenganela kwitu kutenda bhelabhela maghambu uhobhalelu winu ukola namaa na kupalana kwinu kujonjukeka namaa.
\v 4 Nde ndandi tepani tulilumbalila mwehapa pachilanda ja makanisa ghokapi ghaka Chapanga. Tulilumbalila panani ja ntundu monjendalela kuhobhalela na kuhinakila mu mang'ahiku ghokapi na ulali ghomupata.
\p 
\v 5 Ghanihagha ghokapi ghalangiha kubha utemulu waka Chapanga nde wachakaka, na kwa ndandi heji mwehapa anambalangiwaje kubha mpalakiki kupekewa Ukolongwa waka Chapanga, ambau mwehapa mng'ahika kwa ndandi jaki.
\v 6 Chapanga anatenda ghaghapalika: Jombi anaabhalepa mang'ahiku bhala bhabhung'aha mwehapa,
\v 7 na kumpekeha chiheku mwehapa mwemung'ahika papamu na tepani. Chikahi Bambo Yesu panaapitalyaje kuhuma kunani kumahunde papamu na bhatumika bhaki bha kunani bhabhabhi na makili,
\v 8 na mu imuli ya moto. Anaabhalapulaje bhala bhangakummanya Chapanga na ambabhu ngachebhatii Malobhi Manyahi ghaka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo.
\v 9 Utemulu wabhu anaukubha kuyonangeka mileli na kubhekakeka kutali na pamihu jaka Bambo na ulumbalilu wa uwezu waki,
\v 10 chikahi panaahikaje Lichobha lela la kujopalela ulumbalilu kuhuma kwa bhandu bhaki na utopelu kuhuma kwa bhokapi bhabhunhobhalela. Mwehapa nanamu anamkubha papamu nabhu, kwa ndandi muuhobhalili ulandilu ghotundetile.
\p 
\v 11 Ndemana tundobhela chikahi chokapi panga kutonda, nahuli kubha Chapanga apata kumbalanga kubha mpalakiki na ulohakeku waki na kubha kwa uwezu waki apata kuhenga kila lengu linu lamboni na kila litendu lelilonguheka na uhobhalelu winu.
\v 12 Kwa ntundu hoghu, Lihina laka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo analipata ulumbalilu kuhuma kwinu, na mwehapa anampata ulumbalilu kuhuma kwaki kwa chihomu chaka Chapanga witu na chaka Bambo Yesu Kristo.
\c 2
\s1 Muhakau Jola
\p 
\v 1 Bhalongu bhangu bhapalu, kubhokana na kuhika kwaki Bambo witu Yesu Kristo na kulibhongana kwitu papamu palongi jaki: Bhalongu, tundobha namaa,
\v 2 ngamwing'ahika manyata mu mitima, na wala ngamwijeghaleka choghohi kwa roho wala Lilobhi au baluwa yeipwaghakika kubha ihumiki kwitu. Yeipwagha kubha Lichobha laka Bambo lijomwi kuhika.
\v 3 Ngamwijetakela kukoluheka na mundu jokapi kwa ntundu wokapi ghola. Maghambu Lichobha heli ngalihiki mbaka hoti uasi ghola upitalyaje na Muhakau Jola apitalyaje, ambaju ujomukelu waki nde kuyonangeka nakanopi.
\v 4 Jombi anaapengaje na kulikweha panani ja kila chindu chechilowakeka Chapanga au chechijojabhaleka, na hata kulibheka mweni mu Nyumba jaka Chapanga, koni akalitangaza mweni kubha nde Chapanga.
\p 
\v 5 Bho, ngachemkomboka kubha panakabhi papamu na mwehapa nakumpwaghili mambu ghanihagha?
\v 6 Nambu kubhi na chindu chechunhibhalakila sajenu, na mwehapa mchimanyi chindu hechi. Henu, Muhakau hoju anaahyekuliwaje mu chikahi chaki chechipalika.
\v 7 Hata bhela, Muhakau hoju joahiyakiki atenda lihengu sajenu, nambu ngaabhonikani mbaka jola joanhibhalakila abhohakikaje.
\v 8 Panihapa nde Muhakau jola panaapitalyaje, nambu Bambo Yesu paanahikaje anaankomaee kwa mbomu ja ndomu waki na kumuyonanga kwa ung'anyi wa kuhika kwaki.
\v 9 Muhakau hoju anahikaje na makili ghaka Shetani na kutenda kila ntundu wa nginyulila na ngangachu ya upuhi,
\v 10 na kutenda ukoluheku wa kila ntundu kwa bhala bhabhabhi mu nkumbu wa kuhobha. Bhanihabha anabhahobhaje kwa ndandi ngachebhakaujopalili na kuupala uchakaka ghola nahuli bhakengaliwaje.
\v 11 Ndemana Chapanga abhabhekiki pahi ja makili gha kuhobha, nahuli bhauhobhalya upuhi.
\v 12 Mapitalilu ghaki nde kubha bhokapi bhangakuhobhalela uchakaka, nambu bhahekalela mahoku, anabhatemulikaje.
\s1 Muhaghuliki mpataje kukengalewa
\p 
\v 13 Nambu itupalika tepani kunchengula Chapanga machobha ghokapi kwa ndandi jinu, bhalongu mwempalakika na Bambo, kwa ndandi Chapanga akanhawili mwehapa kutumbula pakutumbulila nahuli mkengaliwaje kwa kugholuleka na makili ghaka Roho, mtendakikaje bhandu bhaki bhahuhu kwa kuhobhalela uchakaka.
\v 14 Chapanga akandohili lijambu leniheli kwa indela ja Malobhi Manyahi ghatukuntangazile, akandohiki mpata kushiliki mu ulumbalilu waka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo.
\v 15 Henu, bhalongu bhapalu, njemaje kwa ukangamalu na mughakamulaje namaa mabholu ghala ghatukumboliki ikubhi kwa malobhi gha ndomu au kwa baluwa yitu.
\p 
\v 16 Bambo witu Yesu Kristo mweni na Chapanga Atati witu, joatupaliki na kwa chihomu chaki akatupekihi chiheku cha mileli na lihobhalelu lambone mu chihomu,
\v 17 anjeghala mitima jinu, na kuntenda mkangamalaje mu kila lilobhi na litendu lambone.
\c 3
\s1 Mtulobhilaye kwaka Chapanga
\p 
\v 1 Ujomukelu, bhalongu, mtulobhilaje nahuli kubha ubholu waka Bambo upetalyaje kujaghanila manyata na kujopalewa kwa utopelu ngati bhela moubheli pachilanda jinu.
\v 2 Ndobhaje kabhete nahuli Chapanga atukengalyaje na bhandu bhahakau na bhana mahoku, maghambu nga bhokapi bhabhuhobhalela ubholu hoghu.
\p 
\v 3 Nambu Bambo nde ndongwana, najombi anaampekya ukangamalu mwehapa na kundenda wichu na Muhakau Jola.
\v 4 Na jombi Bambo atupekeha lihobhalelu likolongwa panani jinu, na ngachetubhi na choghohi kubha mtenda na ananjendalya kutenda ghala ghatukumpwaghile.
\p 
\v 5 Bambo ajilonguhaje mitima jinu mu umanyi ukolongwa wa upalu waka Chapanga na mu uhinakalilu ghotupekewa na Kristo.
\s1 Lilakalilu kubhokana na ukata
\p 
\v 6 Bhalongu, tundaghalakila mu Lihina laka Bambo Yesu Kristo, mulijepaje na bhalongu bhokapi bhabhabhi bhakata na ambabhu ngachebhajengalela malaghalakilu ghatukumpekihi mwenga.
\v 7 Maghambu mwehapa mabheni mmanyi ntundu moipalakila kujengalela ulenganesu witu. Tepani ngachetukabhi vakata patukabhi papamu na mwehapa,
\v 8 wala ngachetukalili chilebhi chaka mundu jokapi panga na kulepa. Tukahengiki lihengu kwa ukangamalu na mang'ahiku na ikilu na muhi nahuli ngatwikubha chibwahila kwaka mundu jokapi pachilanda jinu.
\v 9 Tukatendiki anana, nga kwa ndandi ngachetupalika kupata ujangatilu winu, nambu kwa ndandi tupala kumpekeha ulenganesu.
\v 10 Patukabhi papamu na mwehapa, tukampekihi amuli: “Mundu jokapi jwangakupala kuhenga lihengu, ngayikula chilbhi.”
\p 
\v 11 Kwa kubha tujowana kubha bhakumu bha bhandu pachilanda jinu nde bhakata. Ngachebhahenga mahengu ghabhu bheni, nambu bhalijingiha mu mambu gha bhandu bhangi.
\v 12 Henu bhandu ngati bhanihabha tundaghalakila na kundakalila mu lihina laka Bambo Yesu Kristo bhahengaje lihengu kwa kulilongoha bheni na kulipatila ghaghapalika mu matamu ghabhu bhene.
\p 
\v 13 Nambu mwehapa bhalongu, ngamwitonda kutenda ghambone!
\v 14 Ngati mundu jokapi ngacheghatii malaghalakilu ghitu ghaghabhi mu baluwa jenjenu, mulilingalya namaa na mundu hoju. Wala ngamwijangatana naku, nahuli kubha apata kubhona ihoni.
\v 15 Nambu ngamwambalanga kubha adui, nambu mundakalyaje ngati ndongo.
\s1 Ulamukilu wa kujomulela
\p 
\v 16 Henu, Bambo wa lukwali mweni ampekye lukwali chikahi chokapi na kwa kila indela. Bambo akubha na mwehapa mabhokapi.
\p 
\v 17 Nepani Paulo, nundembela ulamukilu ghoni kwa chiwoku changu namwete. Jeniheji nde alama jangu mu baluwa yangu yokapi, kubha anana nde monembela.
\p 
\v 18 Chihomu chaka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo chibya papamu na mwehapa mabhokapi. Amina.
